%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tesla's%20cars%20are%20starting%20to%20look%20pretty%20basic%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20a%20problem%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20Tesla%20Model%203%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e8c8f0ce7f1785b2e7092a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22731%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20released%20the%20Model%203%20in%202017.%3Cp%3EAmber%20Saitta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20been%20years%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-history-founders%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%3C%2Fa%3E%20meaningfully%20changed%20the%20appearance%20of%20many%20of%20its%20cars.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20aging%20vehicles%20have%20a%20negative%20impact%20on%20consumer%20interest%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInvestors%20called%20for%20more%20information%20on%20Tesla's%20new%20products%20during%20the%20earnings%20call%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20a%20problem.%20Its%20cars%20are%20getting%20stale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20there's%20the%20Cybertruck%20%E2%80%94%20if%20you%20want%20a%20large%20truck%20and%20ordered%20early%20enough%20to%20actually%20get%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20people%20looking%20for%20a%20flashy%20new%20design%20in%20Tesla's%20more%20traditional%20car%20lineup%20are%20stuck%20waiting%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Model%20S%20and%20Model%20X%20used%20to%20be%20the%20ultimate%20status%20symbol.%20Some%20of%20the%20first%20Tesla%20owners%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F18-celebrities-who-drive-tesla-cars-2016-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecelebrities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%202020%2C%20TikTok%20star%20Addison%20Rae%20made%20headlines%20when%20she%20was%20spotted%20in%20her%20bright%20pink%20Tesla%20Model%20X.%20Nearly%20four%20years%20later%2C%20the%20car%20doesn't%20look%20much%20different%20and%20s