or%20president.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22871%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jackie%20and%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20after%20voting%20in%20the%201960%20presidential%20election%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669fde0780d4d5da13d6472a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22653%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJackie%20and%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20after%20voting%20in%20the%201960%20presidential%20election.%3Cp%3EMarion%20S%20Trikosko%2FUS%20News%20and%20World%20Report%20Magazine%20Collection%2FPhotoQuest%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20would%20mean%2011%20months%20of%20traveling%20across%20the%20country%20campaigning%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jfklibrary.org%2Flearn%2Fabout-jfk%2Fjfk-in-history%2Fjacqueline-kennedy-in-the-white-house%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKennedy%20Library%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20few%20weeks%20into%20the%20campaign%2C%20Jackie%20became%20pregnant%2C%20meaning%20she%20would%20have%20to%20stay%20home%20in%20Massachusetts%20while%20her%20husband%20hit%20the%20campaign%20trail.%C2%A0Jackie's%20pregnancy%20prevented%20her%20from%20joining%20him%20often%2C%20but%20she%20supported%20him%20by%20doing%20TV%20spots%20and%20magazine%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENovember%208%2C%201960%3A%20Kennedy%20won%20the%20election%20and%20became%20the%2035th%20president%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20with%20Jackie%20by%20his%20side.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22972%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22frank%20sinatra%20and%20jackie%20kennedy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669fde9a80d4d5da13d647a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22729%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrank%20Sinatra%20and%20Jackie%20Kennedy%20attended%20a%20gala%20at%20the%20National%20Guard%20Armory%2C%20Washington%20DC%2C%20on%20January%2019%2C%201961.%3Cp%3EGAB%20Archive%2FRedferns%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20his%20election%2C%20President%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jfklibrary.org%2FJFK%2FJFK-in-History%2FJacqueline-Kennedy-in-the-White-House.aspx%5C%22%3Efirst%20lady%20Jackie%20Kennedy%20became%20a%20powerhouse%20political%20couple%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20observe%20today%20not%20a%20victory%20of%20party%20but%20a%20celebration%20of%20freedom%20%E2%80%94%20symbolizing%20an%20end%20as%20well%20as%20a%20beginning%20%E2%80%94%20signifying%20renewal%20as%20well%20as%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20Kennedy%20said%20in%20a%20speech%20at%20his%20inauguration%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jfklibrary.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2018-05%2FIssue_14_Winter_2011_New_Frontiers.pdf%5C%22%3EKennedy%20Library%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BLet%20the%20word%20go%20forth%20from%20this%20time%20and%20place%2C%20to%20friend%20and%20foe%20alike%2C%20that%20the%20torch%20has%20been%20passed%20to%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20Americans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGene%20Kelly%20and%20Frank%20Sinatra%2C%20who%20helped%20stage%20a%20gala%20the%20night%20before%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20campaign's%20debts%2C%20performed%20over%20inauguration%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENovember%2025%2C%201960%3A%20Their%20son%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%20was%20born.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20F.%20Kennedy%20wheels%20his%20wife%20Jacqueline%20out%20of%20Georgetown%20Hospital%20after%20the%20birth%20of%20their%20son%2C%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%2C%20Jr.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a12a8bfb2b6bedb05a0b72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22481%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJohn%20F.%20Kennedy%20wheels%20his%20wife%20Jacqueline%20out%20of%20Georgetown%20Hospital%20after%20the%20birth%20of%20their%20son%2C%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%2C%20Jr.%3Cp%3EBettmann%20Archive%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20mere%20two%20weeks%20after%20Kennedy%20was%20named%20president-elect%2C%20Jackie%20gave%20birth%20to%20their%20first%20son%2C%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20Jr.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1961%3A%20Jackie%20restored%20and%20renovated%20the%20White%20House%2C%20making%20a%20lasting%20mark%20on%20America's%20most%20famous%20residence.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222430%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jackie%20kennedy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5b9194cd2badb90ec864f4cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShe%20wanted%20to%20incorporate%20history.%3Cp%3EAP%2FWilliam%20J%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20said%20that%20while%20taking%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20White%20House%20as%20a%20child%2C%20Jackie%20wasn't%20impressed%20by%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20outside%2C%20I%20remember%20the%20feeling%20of%20the%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Life%20Magazine%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jfklibrary.org%2Flearn%2Fabout-jfk%2Fjfk-in-history%2Fthe-white-house-restoration%5C%22%3EKennedy%20Library%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BBut%20inside%2C%20all%20I%20remember%20is%20shuffling%20through.%20There%20wasn't%20even%20a%20booklet%20you%20could%20buy.%20Mount%20Vernon%20and%20the%20National%20Gallery%20and%20the%20FBI%20made%20a%20far%20greater%20impression.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20moved%20in%2020%20years%20later%2C%20she%20made%20it%20her%20mission%20to%20re-do%20the%20furnishings.%20According%20to%20the%20Kennedy%20Library%2C%20she%20focused%20on%20collecting%20antiques%20and%20incorporated%20heirloom%20pieces%20to%20emphasize%20the%20home's%20history%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-decor-evolution-2018-2%5C%22%3Erestore%20the%20White%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20%26quot%3Bdecorate%26quot%3B%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Kennedy%20Library%2C%20Kennedy%20had%20already%20spent%20the%20entire%20%2450%2C000%20budget%20allotted%20to%20the%20project%20just%20on%20furnishing%20the%20family's%20private%20quarters.%20However%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20finish%20the%20project%20by%20sourcing%20antiques%20on%20a%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20really%20the%20happiest%20time%20of%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20once%20said%20of%20living%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jfklibrary.org%2Fvisit-museum%2Fexhibits%2Fpast-exhibits%2Fin-her-voice-jacqueline-kennedy-the-white-house-years%5C%22%3EKennedy%20Library%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20when%20we%20were%20the%20closest%20%E2%80%94%20I%20didn't%20realize%20the%20physical%20closeness%20of%20having%20his%20office%20...%20in%20the%20same%20building%20and%20seeing%20him%20so%20many%20times%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMay%2019%2C%201962%3A%20Marilyn%20Monroe%20famously%20sang%20%26quot%3BHappy%20Birthday%26quot%3B%20to%20Kennedy%2C%20sparking%20a%20rumor%20they%20were%20having%20an%20affair.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222319%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jackie%20kenndy%20inauguration%20ball%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5882417cdd0895364e8b4731%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt's%20now%20iconic.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EActor%20Marilyn%20Monroe%20performed%20a%20now-iconic%20rendition%20of%20%26quot%3BHappy%20Birthday%26quot%3B%20to%20him%20while%20she%20wore%C2%A0a%20glittering%2C%20skintight%20dress%20during%20a%20Democratic%20fundraiser%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20Jackie%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaraborrelli%2C%20Jackie%20Kennedy's%20biographer%2C%20claims%20that%20in%20April%201962%2C%20roughly%20a%20month%20before%20Monroe%20performed%20for%20Kennedy%20and%20a%20month%20after%20the%20pair%20had%20engaged%20in%20a%20weekend-long%20affair%2C%20Monroe%20called%20Jackie%20asking%20for%20the%20president%2C%20but%20only%20to%20say%20hello.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20something%20about%20that%20phone%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20Taraborelli%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmarilyn-monroes-jfk-phone-call-haunted-jackie-kennedy-years-stars-death-author-claims%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023.%C2%A0%26quot%3BShe%20later%20told%20family%20members%20that%20there%20was%20a%20haunting%20quality%20to%20Marilyn's%20voice%20that%20really%20stuck%20with%20her.%20And%20it's%20not%20like%20they%20even%20had%20any%20kind%20of%20deep%20conversation.%20But%20it%20was%2010%20years%20of%20wondering%2C%20was%20it%20really%20Marilyn%20Monroe%3F%20And%20that%20buzz%20stayed%20with%20the%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAugust%201963%3A%20Their%20son%20Patrick%20Bouvier%20was%20born%20prematurely.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222757%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jackie%20kennedy%20jfk%20assassination%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5b91aa2d2badb911231a8463%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222068%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJackie%20and%20John%20F.%20Kennedy.%3Cp%3EAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20suffered%20from%20a%20lung%20condition%20and%20died%20two%20days%20later%20on%20August%209%2C%201963%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jfklibrary.org%2Flearn%2Fabout-jfk%2Flife-of-jacqueline-b-kennedy%5C%22%3EKennedy%20Library%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENovember%2022%2C%201963%3A%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20was%20assassinated.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221968%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22JFK%20assassination%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5b91aa2d2badb91