ady%20to%20pick%20someone%20up%20and%20realized%20his%20car%20battery%20was%20dead.%20He%20dropped%20the%20ride%20so%20that%20another%20driver%20could%20fetch%20the%20passenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfterward%2C%20he%20found%20out%20that%20Lyft%20had%20issued%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bwarning%26quot%3B%20curtailing%20his%20ability%20to%20take%20scheduled%20rides%20on%20the%20app.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20see%20anything%20in%20the%20future%20anymore%3B%20I%20don't%20see%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20available%20rides%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Fourteen%20days%20later%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20set%20up%20scheduled%20rides%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20he%20found%2C%20it%20%26quot%3Bjust%20crushes%20your%20earnings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20just%20continue%20to%20do%20the%20scheduled%20rides%2C%20it%20makes%20it%20very%20challenging%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReserving%20scheduled%20rides%20is%20a%20great%20way%20for%20drivers%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20their%20time%20by%20picking%20a%20ride%20time%20and%20route%20that's%20convenient%20for%20them%20in%20advance%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Lyft%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BTo%20ensure%20a%20reliable%20experience%20for%20everyone%2C%20drivers%20should%20only%20reserve%20rides%20they%20can%20complete%20every%20time%2C%20and%20excessive%20cancellations%20may%20result%20in%20temporarily%20reduced%20access%20for%2014%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20gig%20worker%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flyft-driver-explains-how-he-maximizes-earnings-with-sched