.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20rising%20Hinduphobia%20in%20Canada%2C%20the%20BAPS%20Swaminarayan%20Mandir%20was%20vandalised%20with%20alleged%20hateful%20and%20anti-India%20graffiti%20on%20Monday%20morning%20in%20Edmonton%20in%20Alberta%20state%2C%20about%203%2C400%20km%20west-northwest%20of%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandra%20Arya%2C%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20from%20Nepean%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%2C%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20his%20X%20account%20that%20separatist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20of%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%20released%20a%20video%20demanding%20that%20Arya%20and%20his%20Hindu-Canadian%20friends%20go%20back%20to%20India%20after%20he%20(Arya)%20condemned%20the%20vandalism%20of%20the%20Hindu%20temple%20and%20other%20acts%20of%20hate%20and%20violence%20by%20Khalistan%20supporters%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20Hindus%20have%20come%20to%20our%20wonderful%20country%20Canada%20from%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%20From%20every%20country%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20many%20countries%20in%20Africa%20and%20Caribbean%2C%20and%20many%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20we%20have%20come%20here%20and%20Canada%20is%20our%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20Arya%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20Liberal%20Party%2C%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20and%20continue%20to%20make%20immense%20positive%20and%20productive%20contributions%20to%20the%20socio-economic%20development%20of%20Canada.%20With%20our%20long%20history%20of%20Hindu%20culture%20and%20heritage%2C%20we%20have%20enriched%20the%20multicultural%20fabric%20of%20Canada%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20land%20is%20being%20polluted%20by%20Khalistani%20extremists%20abusing%20our%20freedoms%20guaranteed%20by%20our%20Canadian%20Charter%20of%20Rights%2C%26quot%3B%20Arya%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArya's%20statement%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20severe%20strain%20in%20India-Canada%20tie