sting%20system%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354201%2Fhow-to-set-up-start-rainwater-harvesting-affordable-system-diy-steps-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAC%20condensate%20pipes%3C%2Fa%3E%20each%20currently%20cost%20Rs%201%20lakh%20to%20install.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWater%20is%20a%20finite%20resource.%20We%20need%20to%20save%20it%20in%20whatever%20way%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fsmaller-toilet-tanks-could-save-10-of-water%2Farticleshow%2F46843707.cms%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Smaller%20toilet%20tanks%20could%20save%2010%20%25%20of%20water%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20Published%20On%208%20April%2C%202015%20Courtesy%20Times%20Of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fmumbai-to-face-5-water-cut-from-may-30-10-from-june-5-as-lake-levels-fall-430938-2024-05-26%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Mumbai%20to%20face%205%25%20water%20cut%20from%20May%2030%2C%2010%25%20from%20June%205%20as%20lake%20levels%20fall%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20On%2026%20May%2C%202024%20Courtesy%20Business%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721829202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsaprem2-1721819754.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358216%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20drop%20of%20water%20counts.%20This%20should%20be%20a%20mantra%20for%20everyone%20as%20the%20world%20faces%20a%20severe%20water%20shortage.%20Do%20you%20know%20how%20much%20water%20is%20used%20every%20time%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%2