inance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20in%20her%20Budget%20speech%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reduction%20in%20long-term%20capital%20gains%20tax%20rate%20from%2020%20per%20cent%20with%20indexation%20to%2012.5%20per%20cent%20without%20indexation%20for%20real%20estate%20will%20benefit%20in%20almost%20all%20cases%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENominal%20real%20estate%20returns%20are%20generally%20in%20the%20region%20of%2012-16%20per%20cent%20a%20year%2C%20much%20higher%20than%20inflation%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20indexation%20for%20inflation%20is%20in%20the%20region%20of%204-5%20per%20cent%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20period%20of%20holding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20substantial%20tax%20savings%20among%20a%20vast%20majority%20of%20such%20taxpayers%20are%20expected%2C%20they%20said.%20The%20new%20tax%20rate%20without%20indexation%20is%20beneficial%20in%20most%20cases%2C%20the%20Finance%20Ministry%20sources%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20property%20held%20for%20five%20years%2C%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%20is%20beneficial%20when%20the%20property%20appreciates%20at%20least%201.7%20times%20or%20more.%20For%20property%20held%20for%2010%20years%2C%20it%20will%20be%20beneficial%20when%20the%20value%20has%20increased%20to%202.4%20times%20or%20more.%20And%20for%20property%20purchased%20in%202009-10%2C%20if%20value%20has%20increased%20to%204.9%20times%20or%20more%2C%20it%20(new%20tax%20regime)%20is%20beneficial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20only%20when%20the%20returns%20are%20low%20-%20less%20than%209-11%20per%20cent%20a%20year%20-%20that%20the%20earlier%20tax%20rate%20is%20beneficial%2C%20sources%20said.%20But%20such%20low%20returns%20in%20real%20estate%20are%20unrealistic%20and%20rare%2C%20which%20account%20for%20less%20than%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20cases%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20it%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20on%20investment%20of%20capital%20gain%20in%20Section%2054EC%20bonds%20(up%20to%20Rs%2050%20lakh)%20or%20in%20buying%20or%20building%20a%20house%20(up%20to%20Rs%2010%20crore)%2C%20the%20capital%20gain%20is%20exempt%20from%20tax%2C%20subject%20to%20certain%20specified%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%2054EC%20bonds%20or%20capital%20gains%20bonds%20allow%20individuals%20to%20save%20on%20LTCG%20taxes%20incurred%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20property%20or%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20simplification%20of%20any%20tax%20structure%20has%20benefits%20of%20ease%20of%20compliance%20viz%20computation%20filing%2C%20and%20maintenance%20of%20records%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20adding%20this%20also%20removes%20the%20differential%20rates%20for%20various%20classes%20of%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exemption%20limit%20of%20LTCG%20tax%20for%20certain%20financial%20assets%20has%20also%20been%20increased%20from%20Rs%201%20lakh%20to%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20record%20seventh%20Union%20Budget%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20announced%20key%20employment%20schemes%20and%20also%20revised%20the%20tax%20structure%20in%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%2C%20while%20the%20slabs%20in%20the%20old%20regime%20remained%20unchanged.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20congratulated%20her%20for%20a%20balanced%20Budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721828160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F44259kb8_indian-rupee-generic-unsplash_625x300_03_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fscenarios-where-new-long-term-capital-gains-tax-structure-is-beneficial-6179468%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20simplification%20of%20any%20tax%20structure%20is%20that%20it%20removes%20differential%20rates%20for%20various%20classes%20of%20assets%2C%20Finance%20Ministry%20sources%20said%2C%20responding%20to%20feedback%20from%20the%20public%20on%20the%20changes%20in%20LTCG%20tax.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F