eak%2C%20New%20York%20strip%20streak%2C%20and%20lamb%20chops.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20SALT%20Chef's%20Table%20wasn't%20interactive%20enough%20for%20you%2C%20head%20to%20the%20Grill.%20There%2C%20you%20can%20munch%20on%20a%20blooming%20onion%20and%20Ceasar%20salad%20while%20using%20a%20tabletop%20hot%20rock%20to%20cook%20your%20own%20steaks%2C%20lamb%20chops%2C%20and%20shrimp.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELa%20Terraza%2C%20another%20casual%20option%2C%20is%20also%20open%20for%20three%20meals%20of%20the%20day.%20But%20by%20nightfall%2C%20the%20restaurant%20might%20look%20unrecognizable.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22plate%20of%20food%20and%20drinks%20from%20buffet%20on%20Silversea's%20Silver%20Ray%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668302591f0c1cd6d730589c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20buffet%20has%20an%20al%20fresco%20dining%20area.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELa%20Terraza%20is%20home%20to%20the%20ship's%20breakfast%20and%20lunch%20buffet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGuests%20can%20start%20their%20day%20by%20gorging%20on%20classic%20American%20breakfast%20items%2C%20a%20custom%20smoothie%2C%20a%20selection%20of%20tropical%20fruit%2C%20and%20even%20congee.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpt%20for%20one%20of%20the%20outdoor%20tables%20if%20you%20want%20to%20sip%20your%20morning%20cappuccino%20while%20watching%20the%20passing%20waves.%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20the%20afternoon%2C%20the%20congee%20is%20replaced%20by%20platters%20of%20Kaiseki-quality%20sashimi.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22pile%20of%20various%20seafood%20options%20at%20Silver%20Ray's%20buffet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a00edd80d4d5da13d677c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lunchtime%20buffet%20has%20options%20like%20crab%20claws%20and%20shrimp.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20instead%20of%20a%20pile%20of%20bacon%2C%20guests%20can%20pick%20at%20the%20mound%20of%20poached%20seafood%20and%20freshly%20carved%20meats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnd%20the%20buffet%20transforms%20into%20the%20ship's%20go-to%20%C3%A0%20la%20carte%20Italian%20restaurant%20in%20the%20evening.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bread%20and%20small%20appetizers%20on%20%20Silversea's%20Silver%20Ray%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668302811aace5b3ada33bda%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20restaurants%20all%20come%20with%20complimentary%20bread.%20Pictured%20is%20the%20bread%20selection%20from%20La%20Terraza.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELa%20Terraza's%20dinner%20menu%20has%20two%20sections%3A%20one%20%26quot%3Bclassic%26quot%3B%20and%20another%20%26quot%3Badventure.%26quot%3B%20(Have%20you%20noticed%20the%20dual%20menu%20trend%20yet%3F)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPurists%20could%20opt%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20stuffed%20calamari%20and%20pasta%20alla%20norma%20(pasta%20with%20eggplants).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20those%20keen%20on%20the%20adventure%20menu%20%E2%80%94%20which%2C%20according%20to%20Tonet%2C%20was%20designed%20to%20showcase%20contemporary%20Italian%20food%20%E2%80%94%20the%20restaurant%20also%20has%20selections%20like%20whipped%20mortadella%20with%20pecorino%20chips%20and%20grilled%20seabass%20with%20stuffed%20cabbage%20and%20an%20anchovy-Processo%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIf%20you'd%20prefer%20a%20dinner%20and%20a%20show%2C%20head%20to%20Silver%20Note.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22plate%20of%20food%20at%20Silver%20Note%20on%20%20Silversea's%20Silver%20Ray%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668568e21aace5b3ada41a72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESilver%20Note%20has%2054%20seats%20and%20a%20bar%20for%20post-dinner%20drinks%20with%20live%20music.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%2C%20travelers%20are%20serenaded%20by%20a%20jazz%20pianist%20and%20singer%20while%20they%20dine%20on%20small%2C%20refined%20plates.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFood%20options%20are%20as%20casual%20as%20vegetable%20dumplings%20served%20in%20a%20hot%20stone-like%20dish%20and%20as%20whimsical%20as%20a%20triple-chocolate%20dessert%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20a%20swan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20music%20options%2C%20that%20depends%20on%20the%20performers.%20But%20expect%20to%20hear%20classics%20from%20recognizable%20figures%20like%20Frank%20Sinatra%20and%20Bill%20Withers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Arts%20Cafe%20isn't%20technically%20a%20restaurant%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20great%20place%20to%20grab%20a%20quick%20and%20light%20bite.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22composite%20of%20arts%20cafe%20and%20tea%20on%20Silversea's%20Silver%20Ray%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66856a311aace5b3ada41ca7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECoffee%20and%20tea%20are%20complimentary%20on%20Silversea.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Chang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEspresso%20and%20tea%20take%20center%20stage%20at%20the%20daytime%20caf%C3%A9.%20But%20if%20you're%20feeling%20peckish%20before%20dinner%20or%20craving%20a%20do-it-yourself%20afternoon%20tea%2C%20