0the%20Bihar%20government's%20move%20to%20increase%20the%20reservation%20cap%20in%20government%20jobs%20and%20educational%20institutions%20to%2065%25.%20Mr%20Kumar's%20government%20faced%20another%20setback%20this%20week%20when%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20of%20which%20the%20chief%20minister's%20party%2C%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20(JDU)%2C%20is%20also%20a%20part%2C%20said%20%26quot%3Bno%20case%20was%20made%20out%26quot%3B%20to%20give%20special%20status%20to%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Assembly%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%20the%20government%20has%20taken%20steps%20to%20challenge%20the%20Patna%20High%20Court's%20decision%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20but%20that%20failed%20to%20pacify%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20protests%20continued%20during%20the%20chief%20minister's%20speech%2C%20an%20increasingly%20angry%20Mr%20Kumar%20launched%20into%20a%20tirade%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EArre%20mahila%20ho%2C%20kuch%20jaanti%20nahin%20ho%3F%20Arre%20bol%20rahi%20hai%2C%20kahan%20se%20aate%3F%20Yeh%20logo%20ne%20kabhi%20mahila%20ko%20aage%20badhaya%20tha%3F%20Bol%20rahi%20ho%3F%20Faltu.%20Isliye%20ham%20keh%20rahe%20hai%2C%20chup%20chaap%20suno.%20Arre%20kya%20hua%3F%20Sunoge%20nahin%3F%20Hum%20to%20sunayenge.%20Agar%20aap%20nahin%20suniyega%2C%20to%20aap%20logo%20ki%20galti%20hai.%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(You%20are%20a%20woman%2C%20don't%20you%20know%20anything%3F%20Look%2C%20she%20is%20talking.%20Have%20you%20%5Bthe%20opposition%5D%20done%20anything%20for%20women%3F%20We%20will%20talk%20and%20if%20you%20don't%20listen%2C%20its%20your%20%5Bthe%20opposition's%5D%20fault.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20opposition%20erupted%20and%20the%20slogan-shouting%20got%20louder%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20carried%20on%20with%20his%20speech%2C%20insisting%20that%20his%20government%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20for%20the%20disadvantaged%20sections%20of%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20the%20chief%20minister's%20remarks%2C%20Tejashwi%2