%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20Speaker%20speaks%2C%20he%20speaks%20right.%20You%20correct%20yourself.%26quot%3B%20The%20Trinamool%20MP%20stuck%20to%20his%20guns%2C%20prompting%20the%20Speaker%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20speak%2C%20I%20don't%20speak%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Banerjee's%20address%20targeted%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20over%20the%20Budget%20and%20drew%20a%20response%20from%20the%20treasury%20benches%2C%20especially%20BJP%20MPs%20from%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20general%20secretary%20said%20the%20Budget%20lacked%20%26quot%3Bclarity%20of%20vision%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20aimed%20at%20satisfying%20BJP%20coalition%20partners%20rather%20than%20providing%20any%20relief%20to%20the%20country's%20140%20crore%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20budget%20planned%20by%20two%20individuals%20to%20keep%20another%20two%20in%20good%20faith%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bplanned%20by%20two%2C%20executed%20for%20two%26quot%3B.%20Mr%20Banerjee%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Banti-people%26quot%3B%20budget%20was%20crafted%20to%20%26quot%3Bbribe%20two%20political%20parties%20and%20buy%20time%20before%20the%20government%20implodes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20MP%20was%20referring%20to%20TDP%20chief%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20and%20JDU%20leader%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20whose%20support%20gave%20the%20BJP%20the%20required%20numbers%20to%20form%20the%20government%20after%20its%20score%20dropped%20in%20this%20general%20election.%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20argued%20that%20Budget%202024%20was%20generous%20for%20Bihar%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP's%20key%20allies%2C%20but%20other%20states%20got%20nothing%20substantial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20slammed%20the%20Trinamool's%20criticism%20of%20the%20Budget.%20%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20the%20TMC%20questioned%20the%20Budget%2C%20saying%20nothing%20has%20been%20given%20to%20Bengal.%20Let%20me%20highlight%20the%20fact%20that%20several%20schemes%20given%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20have%20not%20even%20been%20implemented%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20And%20you%20have%20the%20audacity%20to%20ask%20me%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Mr%20Banerjee%20threw%20a%20challenge%2C%20daring%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20to%20release%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20how%20much%20money%20the%20Centre%20has%20given%20to%20Bengal%20after%20BJP's%20defeat%20in%20the%202021%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20MP%20said%20the%20Centre%20has%20withheld%20MGNREGA%20funds%20and%20lakhs%20of%20houses%20sanctioned%20under%20the%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana%20in%20Bengal%20are%20waiting%20central%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Banerjee%20said%20that%20money%20that%20should%20have%20been%20used%20to%20build%20homes%20is%20%26quot%3Ballocated%20to%20purchase%20aircraft%20worth%20Rs%208000%20crore%20and%20construct%20palatial%20buildings%20as%20part%20of%20Central%20Vista%20project%20worth%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20while%20poor%20people%20of%20this%20country%20still%20endure%20homelessness%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Mr%20Birla%20said%20members%20must%20avoid%20commenting%20on%20those%20who%20are%20not%20members%20of%20Lok%20Sabha.%20This%20drew%20strong%20remarks%20from%20the%20Trinamool%20members%2C%20prompting%20the%20Speaker%20to%20respond%20sternly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20clarify%2C%20the%20Chair%20said%20we%20should%20not%20comment%20on%20those%20who%20are%20not%20members%20of%20this%20House.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20you%2C%20is%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20a%20member%20of%20this%20House%3F%20Why%20did%20they%20comment%3F%20Please%20maintain%20the%20respect%20of%20your%20Chair%20and%20make%20them%20apologise.%20Then%20I%20will%20continue%2C%20you%20have%20to%20intervene%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Speaker%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20continue%20if%20you%20want%2C%20I%20have%20removed%20her%20name%20from%20the%20record%2C%20you%20cannot%20give%20directions%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%C2%A0At%20the%20end%20of%20Mr%20Banerjee's%20speech%2C%20the%20Speaker%20appealed%20to%20all%20members%20to%20avoid%20making%20remarks%20on%20the%20Chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721820840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ff7mtqb5o_abhishek-banerjee-om-birla_625x300_24_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fom-birla-abhishek-banerjee-budget-2024-trinamool-om-birla-vs-abhishek-banerjee-in-lok-sabha-as-trinamool-shreds-budget-2024-6178549%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20discussion%20on%20Budget%202024%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20today%20witnessed%20a%20sharp%20exchange%20between%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20when%20the%20latter%20claimed%20that%20the%20House%20did%20not%20discuss%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fom-birla-abhishek-banerjee-budget-2024-trinamool-om-birla-vs-abhishek-banerjee-in-lok-sabha-as-trinamool-shreds-budget-2024-6178549%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fom-birla-abhishek-banerjee-budget-2024-trinamool-om-birla-vs-abhishek-banerjee-in-lok-sabha-as-trinamool-shreds-budget-2024-6178549%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fom-birla-abhishek-banerjee-budget-2024-trinamool-om-birla-vs-abhishek-banerjee-in-lok-sabha-as-trinamool-shreds-budget-2024-6178549%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hyundai%20ties%20up%20with%20Charge%20Zone%20for%20charging%20infrastructure%20for%20EV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A172182083600