%3E%20posed%20five%20questions%20to%20the%20government%20Wednesday%20in%20a%20speech%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Finance%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fnirmala-sitharaman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENirmala%20Sitharaman%3C%2Fa%3E%20read%20out%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Funion-budget-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnion%20Budget%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chidambaram%20-%20who%20served%20as%20Finance%20Minister%20in%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20II%20government%20-%20called%20on%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20to%20ensure%20daily%20minimum%20wage%20of%20Rs%20400%20and%20provide%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20for%20MSP%2C%20or%20minimum%20support%20price%2C%20a%20core%20demand%20for%20farmers%20protesting%20since%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20veteran%20also%20demanded%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20write%20off%20the%20unpaid%20balance%20of%20education%20loans%20till%20March%2C%20abolish%20the%20contentious%20Agnipath%20military%20recruitment%20scheme%2C%20and%20scrap%2C%20for%20states%20that%20do%20not%20want%20it%2C%20the%20NEET%20exam%20for%20entrance%20to%20medical%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20threw%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bplease%2C%20copy%20some%20more%26quot%3B%20jibe%20at%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20was%20to%20claims%20the%202024%20Union%20Budget%20borrows%2C%20without%20acknowledgment%2C%20schemes%20proposed%20by%20the%20opposition%20party%20in%20its%20manifesto%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...will%20be%20very%20happy%20to%20support%20you%20(the%20BJP)%2C%20if%20you%20take%20those%20ideas.%20Copying%20is%20not%20prohibited%20in%20this%20House...%20in%20fact%2C%20copying%20is%20encouraged%20and%20rewarded%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20to%20laughter%20from%20opposition%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrisis%20Or%20No%20Crisis%3F%20Jobs%20Are%20The%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chidambaram's%20speech%20rested%20on%20four%20major%20planks%2C%20the%20first%20of%20which%20was%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnemployment%20is%20the%20biggest%20challenge.%20The%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20has%20estimated%20the%20all-India%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20June%202024%20was%209.2%20per%20cent...%26quot%3B%20he%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20earlier%20there%20was%20a%20Production-Linked%20Incentive%20scheme%20(to%20create%20jobs).%20When%20you%20introduced%20an%20employment-linked%20scheme...%20there%20must%20have%20been%20a%20reason.%20I%20suspect%20it%20was%20because%20the%20PLI%20did%20not%20create%20the%20kind%20of%20jobs%20you%20wanted%20to%20create...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chidambaram%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20will%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20tell%20this%20House...%20what%20was%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20PLI%3F%20Once%20we%20know%20the%20outcome...%20we%20can%20look%20ahead%20to%20what%20can%20be%20expected%20from%20the%20ELI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20speech%20Tuesday%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20announced%20three%20ELIs%2C%20including%20a%20five-year%20industry%20internship%20scheme%20(which%20the%20Congress%20claims%20was%20copied)%20in%20association%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20these%20schemes%20would%20create%20jobs%20-%20as%20many%20as%2030%20lakh%20-%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20measures%20were%2C%20predictably%2C%20hailed%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20ministers%2C%20including%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20as%20%26quot%3Bgame-changing%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20have%20been%20panned%20by%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fempower-middle-class-take-education-to-new-scale-pm-mo