ot%3BWe%20bless%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20priest%2C%20whose%20temple%20is%20in%20a%20building%20once%20owned%20by%20Usha's%20family%2C%20the%20Chilukuris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20should%20get%20higher%20positions%20in%20her%20life.%20We%20priests%20offer%20special%20prayers%20for%20Usha%20and%20her%20husband.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha's%20great-grandfather%20moved%20out%20of%20Vadluru%2C%20but%20her%20ancestors%20are%20respected%20in%20the%20village%20as%20academic%20highflyers%20and%20well-versed%20in%20Hindu%20scriptures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20father%20Chilukuri%20Radhakrishnan%20--%20a%20PhD%20holder%20--%20was%20brought%20up%20in%20Chennai%20and%20went%20on%20to%20study%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20He%20returned%20to%20India%20before%20the%20couple%20moved%20back%20across%20the%20Pacific%2C%20and%20Usha%20was%20brought%20up%20in%20suburban%20San%20Diego.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20met%20Vance%20at%20Yale%20Law%20School%20and%20the%20couple%20married%20in%202014.%20They%20have%20three%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHillbilly%20Elegy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%20Vance%20has%20never%20visited%20the%20village%2C%20but%20the%20priest%20said%20her%20father%20last%20came%20around%20three%20years%20ago%20and%20checked%20on%20temple's%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELittle%20is%20known%20about%20Radhakrishnan's%20initial%20years%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20but%20the%20film%20of%20Vance's%20memoirs%2C%20Hillbilly%20Elegy%2C%20refers%20to%20him%20coming%20to%20the%20country%20with%20%26quot%3Bnothing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha's%20character%2C%20played%20by%20Indian%20actor%20Freida%20Pinto%2C%20says%20in%20the%202020%20movie%20now%20streaming%20on%20Netflix%20that%20her%20father%20had%20to%20%26quot%3Bfind%20his%20way%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%20is%20a%20practising%20Hindu%20and%20told%20Fox%20News%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%20that%20the%20faith%20made%20her%20mother%20and%20father%20%26quot%3Bgood%20parents