nded-after-voting-against-two-child-benefit-cap%2Farticleshow%2F111981353.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Flabour-party-mps-suspended-after-voting-against-two-child-benefit-cap%2Famp_articleshow%2F111981353.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Flabour-party-mps-suspended-after-voting-against-two-child-benefit-cap%2Famp_articleshow%2F111981353.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saving%20Kokum%3A%20Why%20a%20Family%20Spent%2015%20Years%20Growing%2010000%20Kokum%20Trees%20%26amp%3B%20Distributed%202%20Lakh%20Saplings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKokum%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20rare%20and%20cherished%20sour-tasting%20fruit%2C%20frequently%20features%20in%20the%20cuisine%20of%20people%20living%20in%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20region%20of%20India.%20Despite%20its%20popularity%2C%20this%20savoury%20fruit%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20scarce%20due%20to%20the%20decline%20in%20its%20plantations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20it%20only%20grew%20wild%20without%20any%20proper%20care%20or%20irrigation.%20They%20were%20almost%20going%20extinct%20when%20my%20father%20started%20to%20grow%20them%20on%20our%20plantation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramesh%20Rai%20(68)%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Narayana%20Rai%20%E2%80%94%20a%20farmer%20from%20Ballikan%20village%20in%20Puttur%2C%20who%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20people%20who%20realised%20the%20decline%20in%20the%20production%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20started%20planting%20the%20fruit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20scientifically%20as%20Garcinia%20indica%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20fruit-bearing%20plant%20in%20the%20mangosteen%20family.%20It%20is%20commonly%20found%20in%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20region%20of%20India.%20Devoured%20for%20its%20savoury%20taste%2C%20it%20is%20also%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3Ebheranda%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Marathi%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekudampuli%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Malayalam%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekodampuli%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Tamil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Narayana%20passed%20away%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20his%20family%2C%20especially%20his%20son%2C%20has%20been%20carrying%20forward%20his%20legacy.%20Narayana%E2%80%99s%20estate%2C%20now%20managed%20by%20his%20son%2C%20boasts%20over%2010%2C000%20blooming%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Etrees%20that%20are%20actively%20producing%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20sat%20down%20with%20Ramesh%20to%20understand%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20vision%20and%20what%20Ramesh%20is%20doing%20to%20take%20it%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20leap%20of%20faith%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20fondly%20recalls%20when%20his%20father%20predicted%20that%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewould%20be%20in%20high%20demand%20in%20the%20future.%20Talking%20about%20the%20history%20of%20the%20estate%20and%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20dream%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20acquired%20our%20property%20in%201950%2C%20transforming%20what%20was%20then%20a%20dense%20forest%20into%20a%20plantation.%20Initially%2C%20we%20planted%20areca%2C%20rubber%2C%20coconut%2C%20jackfruit%2C%20and%20cashew.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ramesh%E2%80%99s%20father%20was%20farming%20different%20plants%2C%20it%20was%20about%2015%20years%20ago%20that%20he%20began%20planting%20Kokum%2C%20anticipating%20its%20future%20demand%20due%20to%20its%20medicinal%20value.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20started%20growing%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecause%20of%20his%20love%20for%20the%20fruit!%20Furthermore%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplants%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20much%20water%20and%20grow%20well%20in%20the%20local%20climate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20that%20his%20father%20planted%20around%2012%2C000%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplants%2C%20of%20which%20approximately%2010%2C000%20have%20survived.%20%3Cem%3EKokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20highly%20sought%20after%20in%20North%20India%20for%20its%20use%20in%20making%20oils%20and%20beverages.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20confident%20that%20the%20price%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewould%20rise%2C%20and%20we%20decided%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20plants%20to%20mature.%20Initially%2C%20the%20price%20was%20around%20Rs%2010%20per%20kg%2C%20but%20it%20has%20now%20risen%20to%20Rs%20120%20to%20130%20per%20kg%2C%20and%20in%20some%20places%2C%20it%20can%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%20300%20per%20kg%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-44-1-1721390537.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Narayan%20Rai%2C%20Ramesh's%20father.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-44-1-1721390537.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-44-1-1721390537-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-44-1-1721390537-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-44-1-1721390537-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-44-1-1721390537-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357728%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENarayan%20Rai%2C%20Ramesh%E2%80%99s%20father.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Narayan%20started%20farming%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eeveryone%20thought%20that%20it%20was%20a%20waste%20of%20time.%20However%2C%20for%20him%2C%20this%20meant%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20native%20tree%2C%20which%20he%20did%20not%20want.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20initial%20challenges%20my%20father%20faced%20were%20significant.%20Farmers%20found%20it%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20a%20simple%20plant%20like%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecould%20solve%20their%20problems.%20Since%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20not%20well-known%20and%20had%20little%20demand%20in%20the%20market%2C%20farmers%20were%20reluctant%20to%20waste%20their%20time%20growing%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%20the%20native%20plant%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20recalls%20that%20his%20father%20Narayan%20took%20it%20upon%20himself%20to%20raise%20awareness%20among%20the%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20demonstrate%20its%20effectiveness%20and%20partner%20with%20various%20organisations%20to%20showcase%20it.%20We%20tried%20to%20explain%20to%20the%20farmers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F266213%2Fkokum-sherbet-recipe-weight-loss-cholesterol-health-science-benefits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20medically%20beneficial%20it%20was%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20took%20around%2036%20to%2060%20months%20for%20the%20farmers%20to%20see%20results%20and%20recognise%20its%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20farmers%20understood%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20idea%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20plant%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Etoo%2C%20he%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20were%20inspired%20after%20seeing%20our%20plantation%20and%20took%20plants%20from%20us.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20we%20have%20distributed%20around%202%2C00%2C000%20saplings%20to%20interested%20farmers.%20We%20charged%20Rs%205%20to%2012%20per%20sapling%2C%20but%20we%20stopped%20nursery%20production%20to%20prevent%20oversaturation%20in%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ramesh%20worked%20as%20a%20hotelier%20for%20most%20of%20his%20life%2C%20he%20is%20now%20planning%20to%20take%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%3Cbr%3Elegacy%20ahead.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20always%20dedicated%20to%20farming%2C%20and%20he%20started%20the%20hotel%20business%20too%20managing%20it%20alongside%20the%20plantation.%20The%20land%20was%20ancestral%20but%20it%20was%20my%20father%20who%20expanded%20it%20to%20200%20sq%20ft%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20farm%20estate.%20We%20live%20on%20the%20estate%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20divide%20my%20time%20between%20the%20hotel%20and%20the%20plantation%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20future%20plans%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%20next%20year%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20focus%20on%20harvesting%20and%20marketing%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20larger%20quantities.%20Labour%20shortages%20have%20limited%20our%20capacity%2C%20but%20we%20are%20addressing%20this%20issue%20by%20bringing%20in%20more%20workers.%20We%20aim%20to%20meet%20the%20current%20high%20market%20demand%20for%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20year%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20harvest%20much%20due%20to%20labour%20shortages%2C%20but%20with%20new%20labour%20strategies%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20overcome%20this%20challenge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20made%20various%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F199656%2Flifestyle-mumbai-ratnagiri-mango-konkan-kokum-juice-summer-beverages-order-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Eproducts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20head%20massage%20oil%2C%20body%20massage%20oil%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F290632%2Fpune-entrepreneur-lalita-khaire-sells-kokanraj-kokum-squash-now-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Ejuice%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Though%20we%20have%20the%20equipment%20and%20facilities%20to%20continue%20production%2C%20we%20have%20not%20actively%20pursued%20it%20since%20his%20passing.%20We%20have%20a%20factory%20and%20machinery%2C%20but%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20continued%20the%20production%20because%20I%20am%20involved%20in%20other%20fields.%20I%20wish%20to%20revive%20that%20one%20day%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-45-1721390491.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ramesh%20has%2010%2C000%20kokum%20trees%20thriving%20on%20his%20estate%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-45-1721390491.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-45-1721390491-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-45-1721390491-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-45-1721390491-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-45-1721390491-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357725%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERamesh%20has%2010%2C000%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%3C%2Fem%3E%20trees%20thriving%20on%20his%20estate%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20has%20also%20hosted%20international%20delegations%20from%20around%2042%20nations%20for%20a%20conference%20organised%20by%20the%20Central%20Plantation%20Research%20Institute%20in%20Kasaragod.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20visited%20our%20plantation%20to%20observe%20and%20learn%20from%20our%20farming%20practices%2C%20especially%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Although%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20regularly%20host%20guests%20at%20the%20estate%2C%20we%20have%20a%20few%20rooms%20in%20our%20old%20house%20for%20o