e-tips%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecycled%20pots.%3C%2Fa%3E%20His%20initiative%20has%20inspired%20neighbours%2C%20sparking%20a%20trend%20of%20roadside%20gardens%20throughout%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManoj%E2%80%99s%20garden%20has%20also%20become%20a%20local%20attraction%2C%20with%20people%20passing%20by%20just%20to%20enjoy%20the%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20personal%20passion%20project%20has%20become%20a%20community%20highlight.%20This%20showcases%20how%20urban%20spaces%20can%20be%20converted%20into%20lush%20gardens%20and%20proves%20that%20anyone%20can%20contribute%20to%20beautifying%20their%20surroundings%2C%20regardless%20of%20space%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20his%20lead%2C%20you%20too%20can%20transform%20vacant%20spaces%20around%20your%20house%20into%20thriving%20gardens%20and%20contribute%20to%20beautifying%20your%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20gardening!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721800949000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358065%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Manoj%20Ranjan's%20family%20moved%20to%20Ranchi%20for%20work%2C%20space%20constraints%20hindered%20his%20gardening%20passion.%20Observing%20people%20dumping%20garbage%20outside%20his%20house%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20turn%20the%20area%20into%20a%20garden.%20Today%2C%20it%20boasts%20200%20plant%20varieties%20and%20has%20become%20a%20local%20attraction%20and%20popular%20selfie%20spot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358065%2Furban-roadside-space-gardening-ranchi-jharkhand-manoj-ranjan-seasonal-flowers-public-places-teacher%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australian%20woman%20gang%20raped%20in%20Paris%20ahead%20of%202024%20Olympics%22%2C%22co