tting%20jobs.%20Many%20companies%20hesitate%20to%20hire%20people%20with%20dwarfism%2C%20worrying%20they%20might%20not%20blend%20well%20with%20other%20employees%20or%20fit%20within%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20infrastructural%20setup%2C%20explains%20Disha%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F327878%2Fsejal-shah-mariposa-foundation-shares-lessons-for-raising-a-child-with-disability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eher%20personal%20experience.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20this%20year%2C%20at%20The%20Club%20Juhu%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20The%20Little%20People%20of%20India%2C%20along%20with%20Vividhataa%2C%20an%20organisation%20focused%20on%20sensitising%20companies%20and%20helping%20them%20fulfil%20their%20diversity%20hiring%20requirements%2C%20conducted%20a%20%E2%80%98Diversity%20Job%20Fair%E2%80%99%20in%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20diverse%20candidates%20ranging%20from%20LGBTQIA%2B%20individuals%2C%20women%20with%20career%20breaks%2C%20army%20veterans%2C%20acid%20attack%20survivors%2C%20and%20people%20from%20other%20socio-economic%20minority%20groups%20participating%20in%20it%2C%20and%20saw%20almost%20500%20people%20get%20interviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20change%20diversity%20ratios%20in%20organisations%20by%20initiating%20conversations%20and%20influencing%20decisions%20by%20showcasing%20that%20hiring%20based%20on%20DEI%20(Diversity%2C%20Equity%20and%20Inclusion)%20is%20the%20way%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ratnaprabha%20Sable%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20managing%20director%20of%20Vividhataa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20open-to-all%20DEI%20seminar%2Fconference%20was%20attended%20by%20corporate%20delegates%20along%20with%20students%2C%20researchers%2C%20experts%2C%20DE%26amp%3BI%20advocates%2C%20and%20similar%20activists%20from%20all%20over%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20panel%20discussions%2C%20fireside%20chats%2C%20and%20interactive%20workshops%20such%20as%20one-on-one%20sign%20language%20were%20held%20at%20the%20event.%20With%20a%20focus%20on%20promoting%20empathy%20and%20understanding%2C%20Vividhataa%20plans%20to%20make%20DEI%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20Indian%20organisations%20and%20global%20MNCs%20across%20India%20through%20its%20initiative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%20in%202020%20and%20traditional%20job%20fairs%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20place%20due%20to%20the%20lockdown%2C%20Vividhataa%20filled%20the%20gap%20by%20launching%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%201st%20Virtual%20Diversity%20Job%20Fair%202020%E2%80%9D%20to%20support%20minority%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20fair%20saw%20lots%20of%20diverse%20candidates%20submitting%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20to%20potential%20employers%20and%20becoming%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20in%20an%20otherwise%20challenging%20job%20market.%20Some%20celebrated%20promising%20job%20offers%2C%20while%20others%20prepared%20for%20successive%20rounds%20of%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20got%20employed%20with%20Amazon%20through%20the%20fair.%20Since%20they%20were%20working%20from%20places%20where%20Amazon%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20offices%2C%20they%20were%20given%20WFH%20opportunities.%20A%20laptop%2C%20a%20table%2C%20and%20every%20other%20work%20equipment%20that%20they%20might%20need%20were%20also%20provided%20by%20the%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20word%20of%20the%20job%20fair%20had%20spread%20around%2C%20organisations%20which%20previously%20were%20not%20big%20on%20hiring%20candidates%20with%20disabilities%20had%20shown%20up%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20long-term%20impact%20of%20equal%20opportunities%20on%20the%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisha%20says%20that%20to%20her%20knowledge%2C%20there%20are%20two%20more%20organisations%20that%20work%20for%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20in%20southern%20India%2C%20but%20are%20only%20restricted%20to%20a%20few%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20The%20Little%20People%20of%20India%20is%20the%20only%20pan-India%20organisation%20working%20for%20the%20community%2C%20and%20that%20Disha%20is%20an%20internationally-acclaimed%20para%20athlete%2C%20her%20organisation%20came%20into%20the%20limelight%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20the%20fair%2C%20everyone%20felt%20safe%20because%20they%20knew%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20judged%20based%20on%20their%20appearance.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254-300x163.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254-500x271.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254-768x417.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254-150x81.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357969%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22586%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20fair%2C%20everyone%20felt%20safe%20because%20they%20knew%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20judged%20based%20on%20their%20appearance.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20represented%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20in%20various%20marathons.%20At%20every%20chance%20I%20got%2C%20I%20advocated%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20people%20with%20dwarfism%2C%20and%20others%20have%20seen%20our%20community%20grow%20ever%20since%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20talking%20about%20the%20job%20fair%2C%20Disha%20says%20that%20in%20an%20average%20scenario%2C%20if%20there%20are%2050%20applicants%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311815%2Fkerala-woman-with-disability-rejected-from-jobs-launched-organic-food-biz-geetha-saleesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20among%20them%20has%20a%20disability%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%2Fshe%20may%20feel%20lost.%20But%20at%20the%20fair%2C%20everyone%20felt%20safe%20because%20they%20knew%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20judged%20based%20on%20their%20appearance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20know%20that%20their%20education%2C%20experience%2C%20and%20what%20they%20bring%20to%20the%20table%20is%20all%20that%20matters%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVilas%20Dahipale%2C%20an%20LPI%20member%20based%20in%20Pune%20who%20was%20born%20with%20dwarfism%2C%20holds%20an%20engineering%20degree%20but%20got%20rejected%20by%20over%2020%20companies.%20After%20a%20relative%20helped%20him%20get%20a%20job%2C%20he%20worked%20without%20a%20salary%20for%20the%20first%20few%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20he%20updated%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20with%20skills%20such%20as%20automation%20testing%2C%20and%20after%20a%20span%20of%20over%203%20years%2C%20he%20has%20now%20been%20offered%20a%20job%20at%20Accenture%20with%20a%20pick-up%2Fdrop-off%20service%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20job%20fair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20companies%20take%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20online%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20actually%20consider%20you%20as%20a%20candidate%20if%20you%20have%20a%20disability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20After%20switching%20various%20fields%20upon%20realising%20his%20limitations%20(for%20instance%2C%20field%20work%20was%20taxing%20for%20Vilas%20given%20his%20height)%2C%20he%20decided%20that%20he%20could%20only%20do%20office-based%20or%20remote%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20admits%20that%20he%20was%20initially%20unaware%20that%20companies%20offer%20jobs%20to%20people%20with%20disabilities.%20%E2%80%9CLearning%20that%20there%20was%20a%20separate%20%E2%80%98handicapped%E2%80%99%20category%20on%20job%20portals%20was%20a%20revelation%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20admits%20Vilas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20revealed%20his%20condition%20on%20job%20portals%2C%20he%20started%20receiving%20calls%20from%20employees%20who%20were%20looking%20to%20hire%20handicapped%20candidates.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20saddest%20part%20is%20that%20most%20companies%20who%20are%20open%20to%20hiring%20candidates%20with%20disabilities%20are%20MNCs%20from%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%2C%20and%20not%20Indian%20companies%2C%E2%80%9D%20rues%20Vilas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakruthi%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20LPI%20member%20born%20with%20dwarfism%2C%20is%20all%20set%20to%20do%20her%20postgraduate%20diploma%20in%20management.%20She%20says%20that%20she%20is%20afraid%20employers%20won%E2%80%99t%20think%20of%20her%20as%20a%20real%20candidate%20due%20to%20her%20height%2C%20but%20the%20silver%20lining%20is%20that%20she%20has%20the%20job%20fair%20to%20look%20forward%20to%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20done%20two%20internships%20during%20her%20undergraduate%20at%20Teresian%20College%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20she%20admits%20to%20her%20classmates%20taking%20pictures%20of%20her%20and%20mocking%20her%20for%20her%20height%2C%20which%20went%20on%20to%20affect%20her%20marks%20and%20her%20morale.%20But%20she%20took%20a%20stand%20for%20herself%20which%20helped%20her%20blossom%20personally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20message%20to%20her%20bullies%3F%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20treat%20anyone%20else%20the%20way%20you%20treated%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Disha%20shares%20how%20she%20got%20her%20first%20job%20offer%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20a%20small%20ICICI%20home-loan%20third-party%20office%20after%20giving%2017%20interviews.%20When%20she%20finished%20her%20graduation%20in%20early%202000s%2C%20there%20were%20no%20online%20job%20portals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20only%20classified%20columns%20in%20newspapers%2C%20and%20walk-in%20interviews%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecounting%20an%20experience%20of%20going%20to%20Sab%20TV%20for%20an%20interview%2C%20the%20response%20she%20was%20met%20was%20this%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESab%20kuch%20theek%20hai%2C%20par%20aap%20thode%20alag%20ho%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Everything%20is%20fine%2C%20but%20you%20are%20a%20bit%20different).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20told%20that%20the%20employees%20at%20the%20company%20may%20not%20be%20comfortable%20with%20her%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHiring%20candidates%20with%20disabilities%20is%20not%20something%20that%20most%20corporate%20organisations%20in%20India%20are%20too%20keen%20on%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20it%20as%20directly%20generating%20income%20or%20business%20for%20their%20companies%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ratnaprabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20social%20awareness%20on%20disability%20has%20increased%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20organisations%20have%20understood%20the%20need%20to%20back%20diverse%20candidates%20and%20have%20started%20to%20more%20thoroughly%20follow%20the%20ES%26amp%3BT%20(Employments%20through%20Skills%2C%20Training%20and%20Placement)%20guidelines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConducting%20a%20job%20fair%20which%20spreads%20awareness%20on%20issues%20like%20disabilities%2C%20socio-economic%20marginalisation%20and%20caste%2C%20something%20that%20most%20organisations%20shy%20away%20from%2C%20was%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20admits%20Ratnaprabh