3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20office%20is%20located%20on%20a%206.5-acre%20site%20with%20a%20lake%20on%20the%20eastern%20side.%20The%20design%20takes%20full%20advantage%20of%20the%20site%E2%80%99s%20natural%20features.%20The%20building%20is%20oriented%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20its%20longer%20side%20faces%20north-south%2C%20allowing%20glare-free%20natural%20light%20into%20the%20space.%20Porosity%20in%20planning%20and%20form%20allows%20continuous%20movement%20of%20breeze%2C%20ensuring%20natural%20ventilation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwetha%20also%20emphasises%20that%20she%20focused%20on%20merging%20aesthetics%20with%20sustainability.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20three-floor%20structure%20has%20terrace%20gardens%20at%20every%20level%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20cascading%20rice%20fields%2C%E2%80%9D%20Swetha%20notes.%20The%20terraces%20provide%20insulation%20to%20the%20office%20spaces%20below%2C%20reducing%20heat%20and%20aligning%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20sustainable%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBpit4xKHeam%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBpit4xKHeam%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cd