%20%3Cem%3Etandoor%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebrushed%20with%20%3Cem%3Eghee%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20served%20in%20a%20smooth%20tomato-cream%20sauce.%20Food%20aficionados%2C%20governments%2C%20historians%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Britain%20and%20India%20have%20constantly%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20tug-of-war%20to%20dispute%20the%20origins%20of%20the%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Echicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20milder%20take%20on%20this%2C%20as%20someone%20neutral%20to%20the%20argument%2C%20would%20suggest%20is%20that%20the%20gravy%20is%20a%20cross-fertilisation%20of%20ideas%20and%20a%20genius%20of%20many%20minds.%20Today%2C%20we%20explore%20this%20diplomatic%20stance%2C%20while%20also%20hearing%20out%20what%20each%20side%20has%20to%20say%20about%20the%20%3Cem%3Etikka%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20accepted%20story%20is%20also%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F251933%2Fsakshi-deepa-guha-bengali-love-cafe-mother-daughter-gurugram-food-startup-authentic-homemade-bengali-food-tiffin-services-zomato-swiggy-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eculturally%20vibrant%20%3C%2Fa%3Eone.%20It%20involves%20a%20%3Cem%3EBangladeshi%3C%2Fem%3E%20chef%20at%20a%20Scottish%20restaurant%20and%20(multiple%20sources%20suggest%20different%20professions)%20a%20hungry%20bus%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20rainy%20day%20in%201971%2C%20Chef%20Ali%20Ahmed%20Aslam%20cooked%20up%20a%20dish%20(chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%3C%2Fem%3E)%20for%20a%20customer%20who%20stopped%20by%20the%20Shish%20Mahal%20restaurant%20in%20Glasgow%2C%20Scotland.%20The%20customer%20did%20not%20seem%20too%20appeased%20by%20the%20order%20and%20sent%20it%20back%20to%20the%20kitchens%20terming%20it%20%E2%80%9Ctoo%20dry%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChannelling%20his%20curatorial%20skills%2C%20Chef%20Ali%20decided%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20dish%E2%80%99s%20lacking%20moisture%20with%20a%20creamy%20tomato%20sou