ipe%20of%20the%20butter%20chicken.%20I%20think%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eactually%20happened%20here%20in%20the%20UK.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20people%20know%20that%20this%20was%20the%20dish%20that%20was%20invented%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20culinary%20experts%20aren%E2%80%99t%20backing%20down%20from%20whose%20brainchild%20the%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereally%20was%2C%20it%20seems%20foodies%20around%20the%20world%20aren%E2%80%99t%20too%20bothered%20by%20this.%20As%20long%20as%20the%20table%20has%20a%20good%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%20As%20a%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%20dating%20back%20to%202007%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20organisers%20of%20the%20National%20Curry%20Week%20have%20estimated%20that%20if%20all%20the%20portions%20of%20chicken%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20masala%3C%2Fem%3E%20consumed%20annually%20in%20the%20country%20were%20stacked%20on%20top%20of%20one%20another%2C%20they%20would%20form%20a%20tower%202%2C770%20times%20taller%20than%20the%20Greenwich%20Millenium%20Dome.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20chance%20that%20the%20present%20statistics%20have%20outranked%20these.%20Questions%20about%20the%20ethnicity%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Etikka%20%3C%2Fem%3Emight%20always%20remain%20unanswered.%20But%20we%20can%20all%20agree%20on%20one%20thing%3B%20whoever%20came%20up%20with%20this%20ingenious%2C%20humble%2C%20versatile%20dish%20has%20a%20special%20place%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhomegrown.co.in%2Fhomegrown-explore%2Fthe-controversial-history-of-chicken-tikka-masala%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Controversial%20History%20Of%20Chicken%